ty\"\":\"\"warning\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-14T05:13:33.28529037Z\"\"}\",出现次数:10\naiops-k8s-07,frontend,frontend-1,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"failed to get ads: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = transport is closing\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"4df71a45-42b6-434d-8215-b1318428a991\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"GET\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/product/0PUK6V6EV0\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"failed to retrieve ads\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"b9a9508d-318d-4a46-b8dc-1e577344efb4\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"warning\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-14T05:10:29.625928845Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-07,frontend,frontend-1,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"failed to get ads: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.8.174:9555: connect: connection refused\\\"\"\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"220ec4c0-07c9-4127-8f7f-8606037297d0\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"GET\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/product/L9ECAV7KIM\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"failed to retrieve ads\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"edfc7f50-47d0-46c5-a482-a044e9480f30\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"warning\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-14T05:12:34.904412632Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["frontend-0", "frontend-2", "frontend-1"], "service_name": ["frontend"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-03", "aiops-k8s-04", "aiops-k8s-07"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault was detected from 2025-06-14T05:10:28Z to 2025-06-14T05:31:28Z. Please analyze its root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-14 05:10:28+00:00 to 2025-06-14 05:31:28+00:00"}, "log_data_collected": true, "log_analysis_findings": "根据获取的错误日志信息，涉及的异常主要包含以下特点：\n\n### 分析结果\n\n**错误关键词**:\n- **Connection Refused**: 日志中多次出现连接拒绝错误，涉及到以下错误信息：`transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.8.174:9555: connect: connection refused`\n- **Transport Errors**: 包含 `transport: Error while dialing` 的日志条目。\n- **Service Unavailable**: 包含 `rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error` 的描述。\n- **Transport Closing**: 少量日志中出现 `desc = transport is closing`。\n\n**公共嫌疑人**:\n- 前端服务频繁报错，未能成功检索广告数据，显然其中涉及到与一个特定 IP 地址的连接问题。\n\n**识别模式**:\n- **Port Misconfiguration**: 错误日志中表现出典型的端口错误配置特征。多个前端 pod 报告了无法连接到目标服务的特定端口，从而导致服务不可用。\n\n### 输出JSON\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"port\", \"connection refused\", \"transport\", \"Error while dialing\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"connection error due to port misconfiguration causing frontend service failure\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.8.174:9555: connect: connection refused\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n继续调查和验证这些连接问题是详细解决故障的关键。建议检查被调用的服务是否端口配置正确，并确保网络策略允许通信。", "trace_analysis_findings": "通过数据采集分析了 UUID 为 de83df2d-281 的异常，并发现以下内容：\n\n### 异常调用链数据分析\n\n1. **延迟倍数显著增加的调用链**:\n   - **hipstershop.CartService/EmptyCart (checkoutservice-0 -> cartservice-0)**: 延迟从正常的 2569.2ms 增加到异常的 32456.5ms，倍数约为 12.63。\n   - **hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct (frontend-1 -> productcatalogservice-1)**: 延迟从正常的 9209.96ms 增加到异常的 11133.45ms，倍数约为 1.21（虽未超出 2 倍，但属于可疑增长）。\n\n2. **异常调用频率**:\n   - **hipstershop.AdService/GetAds**: 主要发生在 `frontend` 到自身的调用链，出现了高频的连接拒绝错误，这可能是根本问题。\n\n3. **连接拒绝错误统计**:\n   - **hipstershop.AdService/GetAds**\n     - 出现 \"connection refused\" 错误的次数较高，总计 4756 次。\n\n### 根因定位\n\n- `hipstershop.AdService/GetAds` 中的连接错误可能是许多延迟增加的触发点，导致其他调用链如 `hipstershop.CartService` 和 `hipstershop.ProductCatalogService` 中的异常。\n\n### 建议的重点关注对象\n\n- **广告服务 (AdService)** 的连接问题可能是问题的起始点：注意连接错误和系统资源配置。\n- **购物车服务 (CartService)** 和 **产品目录服务 (ProductCatalogService)** 的处理时间增加可能是服务不稳定或下游服务 (比如 Redis) 的响应问题。\n\n### JSON 输出格式\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"frontend->frontend\", \"checkoutservice->cartservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"\\\"connection error: desc = \\\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp... connect: connection refused\\\"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Normal: 2569.2ms, Anomaly: 32456.5ms\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n请针对广告服务的连接问题进行深入调查，可能需要评估资源和网络配置。", "metric_analysis_findings": "从采集的数据中，我们可以发现以下异常调用链及相关指标：\n\n### 检测到的异常指标\n1. **Pod CPU Usage:**\n   - `adservice-1` 的 `pod_cpu_usage` 显著变化，故障中断期间中断为 `0`，正常时为 `0.01`，变化率为 `2.0`。\n\n2. **Service Request/Response Times:**\n   - `emailservice-1` 和 `frontend-1` 等多个服务的 `rrt_max` 值有显著上升，特别是 `emailservice` 和 `adservice`。\n\n3. **Node Memory Usage:**\n   - `aiops-k8s-01` 节点的 `node_memory_usage_rate` 显著升高，从正常的 `29.4` 增至故障期间的 `48.12`，变化率为 `0.483`。\n\n### 故障假设\n- **Component: `aiops-k8s-01`**\n  - **Reason:** 该节点的 `node_memory_usage_rate` 增加可能是由于其中一个或多个Pod在消耗大量内存，但无单个Pod显示出显著异常的资源使用。\n  - **Evidence:** `node_memory_usage_rate` 从 `29.4` 增至 `48.12`。\n\n- **Component: `adservice-1`**\n  - **Reason:** `adservice-1` 的 `pod_cpu_usage` 显著波动，可能由于Pod挂起或退出。\n  - **Evidence:** `pod_cpu_usage` 从 `0.01` 变为 `0`。\n\n- **Component: `emailservice-1`**\n  - **Reason:** 服务请求响应时间显著增加，可能表现出性能问题。\n  - **Evidence:** `rrt_max` 从 `3520.0` 增至 `3573.0`，且P99从 `7167.57` 增至 `64293.2`。\n\n### 发现总结\n这些指标表明该故障可能是由于节点资源紧张和特定Pod异常导致服务性能的退化。我们建议优先检查 `aiops-k8s-01` 节点以判定是否有系统进程异常或硬件问题，同时检查 `adservice-1` 和 `emailservice-1` Pod 的日志以进一步确认根本原因。"}
